ence option is turned off OR not included in the MR configuration.  If this occurs, it can result in overheating of an MR conditional implant.", "date_initiated": "2024-06-14", "status": "Open, Classified", "root_cause": "Device Design", "product_description": "SIGNA Hero, with affected software versions:  PX29.1, MR30.0, MR30.1; Nuclear Magnetic Resonance Imaging System"}], "trials": []}